original_title: Di Blasio: El Piano De America
overview: Combining the genres of classical and power pop, Raul Di Blasio presents for you a selection of his music videos. A huge star in the world of Latin music, included here is his duet with Michael Bolton "El Dia Que Me Quieras" and ten other videos, as well as a discography.
title: Di Blasio: El Piano De America
